prompts.logic_claims_user_template:
Extraction mode: BALANCED.

Title: {{title}}
Authors: {{authors}}
Year: {{year}}
DOI: {{doi}}

Allowed step types: {{step_ids}}
Allowed claim kinds: {{kind_ids}}
Target claims: {{cmin}}-{{cmax}}

Paper text:
{{body}}

Output JSON schema:
{
  "logic": {"<StepType>":{"summary":"2-6 full sentences...","confidence":0.0}},
  "claims": [{"text":"1-2 full sentences...","confidence":0.0,"step_type":"<StepType>","claim_kinds":["KindA","KindB"]}]
}

prompts.evidence_pick_user_template:
Mode: BALANCED evidence mapping.
Pick {{emin}}-{{emax}} chunk_id(s) from candidates per claim.
If none strongly supports, return best 1 and weak=true.

Input JSON:
{{payload_json}}

Output JSON schema: { "items": [ {"claim_key":"...","evidence_chunk_ids":["..."],"weak":false} ] }

prompts.phase1_logic_bind_user_template:
Mode: BALANCED logic binding.
Allowed step types: {{step_ids}}

Logic summaries JSON:
{{logic_brief_json}}

Chunk catalog JSON:
{{chunks_json}}

Output JSON schema: { "items": [ {"step_type":"Background","evidence_chunk_ids":["c1","c2"],"evidence_weak":false} ] }

prompts.phase1_chunk_claim_extract_user_template:
Mode: BALANCED chunk extraction.
Allowed step types: {{step_ids}}
Allowed claim kinds: {{kind_ids}}
Max claims: {{max_claims}}

Chunk text:
{{chunk_text}}

Output JSON schema: { "claims": [ {"text":"...","evidence_quote":"...","step_type":"Background","claim_kinds":["Definition"],"confidence":0.0} ] }

prompts.citation_purpose_batch_user_template:
Mode: BALANCED citation purpose classification.
Citing paper title: {{citing_title}}

Input JSON:
{{cites_json}}

Allowed labels: {{allowed_labels}}

Output JSON schema: { "cites": [ {"cited_paper_id":"doi:10....","labels":["MethodUse"],"scores":[0.72]} ] }
